name: Bataille du Colibri
description:
Battle of the Hummingbird

Tattooed Torso. Taking inspiration from Peter Blake’s pieces of a similar nature, using the body as a place to contextualise and bring together ideas and sketches. Exploring themes of internal conflict and self love/hate. 
Lots of hidden details and references, as always.

Digital Illustration 3543 × 3543px
